        <section class="help-section">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>How do I book a package?</h3>
                <p>Simply browse our available packages on the dashboard, click on "Book Now" for your desired package, fill in your details, and confirm your booking. You'll need to create an account or login first.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Can I modify my booking?</h3>
                <p>Yes! Contact our support team at support@journeysphere.com or call +91 1800-123-4567 to modify your booking. Please note that modifications are subject to availability and may incur additional charges.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>What is the cancellation policy?</h3>
                <p>Cancellations made 30 days before departure: 100% refund<br>
                Cancellations made 15-29 days before: 50% refund<br>
                Cancellations made less than 15 days: No refund</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Are meals included in the packages?</h3>
                <p>Meal inclusions vary by package. Check the package details or contact us for specific information about what's included in your chosen package.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>What documents do I need for travel?</h3>
                <p>For domestic travel, a valid government-issued ID is required. For international travel, you'll need a valid passport and may require a visa depending on the destination.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Is travel insurance included?</h3>
                <p>Travel insurance is not included by default but can be added to your booking. We highly recommend purchasing travel insurance for your peace of mind.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>How do I create an account?</h3>
                <p>Click on "Sign Up" in the navigation menu, fill in your details including name, email, and password, and click "Sign Up". You'll be logged in automatically and can start booking!</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Can I book for a group?</h3>
                <p>Yes! When booking, simply specify the number of travellers. For large groups (more than 20 people), please contact us directly for special group rates.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        
